Jade
****

   Jade is a highly flexible Emacs-style text editor for X11 (on Unix)
and AmigaDOS.

   This is Edition 1.3 of its documentation, last updated 7 October
1994 for Jade version 3.2.


 @{" Copying " Link "Copying"}                      Distribution conditions
